- [ ] **to get started**
  - [X] Create a tag according to the [semantic versioning](https://semver.org/) compliant with the following syntax 1.a.n where: a: approach number [1..3], n: any number you like
  - [X] program text is in C#
  - [X] build succeeded
  - [X] all UTs are green
- [X] program has layered architecture and contains at least `presentation`, `logic`, and `data` layers
- [ ] **Data Layer**
  - [X] responsibility of this layer is to represent balls
  - [X] the layer is clearly stated **using language terms only**
  - [X] the layer doesn't depend on external data, for example, a database, or file.
  - [X] the API is clearly stated
  - [X] the API is abstract
- [ ] **Logic Layer**
  - [X] `Logic` layer is clearly stated **using language terms only**
  - [X] `Logic` API is clearly stated and abstract
  - [X] `Logic` uses only the abstract `Data` layer API
- [ ] **Presentation Layer**
  - [X] `Presentation` layer is clearly stated **using language terms only**
  - [X] `Presentation` uses only the abstract `Logic` layer API
  - [X] MVVM and XAML are applied to implement GUI
  - [X] reactive and interactive user interaction for user (operator) communication
  - [X] the graphical user interface (GUI) must be scaled appropriately
- [X] Fulfill functional requirements of the task
- [X] **Testing**
  - [X] Unit Test - layers are tested independently using abstract API and Dependency injection (external package is not allowed)
  - [X] Mock (external package) must not be used for testing purposes
